title.narrative: WAPP: The First Phase of the Inter-Zonal Transmission Hub Project of the WAPP (APL3) Program

description.narrative: The development objective of the first phase of the Inter-Zonal Transmission Hub Project under the WAPP APL3 is to reduce the cost of and improve security of electricity supply to Burkina Faso, while increasing Ghana's electricity export capacity.
